---
import '../styles/base.css';
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
    <meta name="description" content="Clarity. is a premium Strategic Insight-as-a-Service partner.  Support plans that equip product and enterprise leaders with fast, actionable answers." />
    <meta name="author" content="Your Company or Name" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Clarity. — Insight-as-a-Service" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Clarity. helps leaders move faster with structured insights — not assumptions. Join the waitlist." />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://yourdomain.com" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://yourdomain.com/og-image.jpg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Clarity. — Insight-as-a-Service</title>
  </head>
  <body class="text-gray-900 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-[#EAF6FB] dark:from-[#1A1A1A] dark:to-[#2C3E50] dark:text-white">
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">Clarity. Without the Noise.</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">Join the waitlist for Clarity. — your Strategic Insight-as-a-Service Partner. Clear support plans designed for product and enterprise leaders who need faster answers, tighter focus, and confident decisions.</p>

      <form id="waitlist-form" class="space-y-4 max-w-md mx-auto">
        <input
          type="email"
          name="email"
          required
          placeholder="you@example.com"
          class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:ring-blue-200"
        />
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="w-full py-2 px-4 bg-black text-white rounded font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 transition"
        >
          Join the Waitlist
        </button>
      </form>
      <p id="response" class="mt-4 text-green-600"></p>

      <script>
        document.getElementById('waitlist-form').addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
          e.preventDefault();
          const email = e.target.email.value;
          const res = await fetch('API_URL_HERE', {
            method: 'POST',
            body: JSON.stringify({ email }),
            headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
          });
          if (res.ok) {
            window.location.href = '/thank-you';
          } else {
            document.getElementById('response').textContent = 'Something went wrong. Please try again.';
          }
        });
      </script>
    <section class="mt-16">
  <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 mb-4">Trusted by product leaders at</p>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 opacity-80">
    <img src="/placeholder-logo1.svg" alt="Logo 1" class="h-8" />
    <img src="/placeholder-logo2.svg" alt="Logo 2" class="h-8" />
    <img src="/placeholder-logo3.svg" alt="Logo 3" class="h-8" />
    <img src="/placeholder-logo4.svg" alt="Logo 4" class="h-8" />
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mt-20 text-left">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Why Insight-as-a-Service?</h2>
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Outcome Clarity.</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Know exactly what to build and why — no more guessing, scope creep, or building the wrong thing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Embedded Expertise</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Our team integrates into yours — no bloated decks or outside observers, just delivery-ready insight.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Predictable Cost</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Frictionless support plans — fixed scope, high impact, no unexpected invoices.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mt-20 text-center">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">What Our Clients Say</h2>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <blockquote class="italic text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
      “Before working with them, we were guessing what to build. Their Discovery process gave us clarity, confidence, and speed — we cut 3 months off our roadmap.”
    </blockquote>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">— Head of Product, Fintech Scaleup</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mt-20 bg-gray-900 text-white py-12 px-6 rounded-lg text-center">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Still thinking about it?</h2>
  <p class="mb-6 text-lg">The sooner you're on the list, the sooner you'll stop wasting time on the wrong problems. Join now — no fluff, no spam, just Clarity.</p>
  <a href="#waitlist-form" class="inline-block bg-white text-black font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-gray-200 transition">Join the Waitlist</a>
</section>
<div class="mt-16">
  <style>
    .logo-light {
      display: block;
    }
    .logo-dark {
      display: none;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .logo-light {
        display: none;
      }
      .logo-dark {
        display: block;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Light Mode Logo -->
  <svg class="logo-light mx-auto" viewBox="0 0 400 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet">
    <defs>
      <linearGradient id="lightGradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#FFFFFF" />
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#EAF6FB" />
      </linearGradient>
    </defs>
    <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#lightGradient)" />
    <text x="50%" y="50%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="middle"
          font-family="Inter, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"
          font-size="48" font-weight="700" fill="#333">
      Clarity.
    </text>
  </svg>

  <!-- Dark Mode Logo -->
  <svg class="logo-dark mx-auto" viewBox="0 0 400 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet">
    <defs>
      <linearGradient id="darkGradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#1A1A1A" />
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#2C3E50" />
      </linearGradient>
    </defs>
    <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#darkGradient)" />
    <text x="50%" y="50%" dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="middle"
          font-family="Inter, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"
          font-size="48" font-weight="700" fill="#F2F2F2">
      Clarity.
    </text>
  </svg>
</div>
</main>
  </body>
</html>
